content.rendered:
A partnership that drives success

By joining the SUSO Partner Club, you get access to the training, support and resources to ensure your clients succeed in SEO. Take advantage of this free resource and level up your team’s digital skillset today! Your clients and staff will love you for it.

Join SUSO Partner Club

Access benefits designed for your team

Education and Insights

Access to weekly invite-only webinars as well as agency-specific in-person and remote workshops

Analysis & Reports

Insightful analysis and strategic recommendations that will help your clients grow their traffic

Helpdesk Support

Need help with a specific SEO question? Message our helpdesk and receive a quick and detailed response to your query

Education and Insights

Weekly 30-minute webinars

Each week we tackle a new SEO topic in an informal, interactive setting. The curriculum is frequently changing in line with the fast-paced evolution of our industry. We tailor content based on the feedback of SUSO Partner Club members and take pride in making the complexities of SEO, digestible and easy to understand without oversimplifying the topics.

In-person workshops

Partner Club members can take advantage of in-person workshops where a senior member of SUSO’s training team delivers a customised session for your team. Workshops typically last between 1 to 2 hours. Each session is unique and tailored to your agency’s requirements.

News & Insights

Be the first to receive news of successful strategies that SUSO are using and insights into how Google’s algorithm works. Our team analyses hundreds of sites every week and we report back key findings to our partner network.

Free Analysis & Reports

Health Reports

Take advantage of our free SEO health reports. The reports are custom, typically 20 pages, with quick-win SEO tips that will help your clients understand how they can get more business with the help of SEO. These reports can be white-labeled and delivered in your branding.

Pitch Support

If you want to pitch SEO services to your client and need help with a proposal, SUSO can support you. We can craft the perfect SEO pitch for you with all the essential data and commentary included.

Full Audit Token

Partners that show 3 months of commitment to the Club will receive 1 token for a full complimentary SEO audit for a website of their choice. Our audits are a popular product, and we recommend a minimum sell-on value of $2000.

Helpdesk & Drop-in Support

SUSO Helpdesk

We know finding the correct answer online isn’t always so simple when it comes to SEO. If you need help just email us on helpdesk@susodigital.com and by simply quoting the name of your agency along with your specific SEO query, you’ll receive a detailed answer from the appropriate expert at SUSO within 24 hours.

Friday Drop-in Sessions

Every Friday at 2 pm to 3 pm GMT, a senior member of SUSO’s training team is available live to answer any of your questions. Simply hop on to the video link and get chatting.

“We created the SUSO Partner Club to educate our partners, not sell to them. So what’s in it for SUSO? What’s the catch? There is none. We simply want to be known as the best SEO agency on the planet whether or not you do business with us. We feel the best way to demonstrate this is by giving back and sharing our expert knowledge and insights with as many companies as we can.”

Will Bagnall, SUSO Founder & CEO

A Completely
Free Resource

No financial or time commitment is required to be a SUSO club member. Sign your team up and they’ll receive all the benefits. Explore our content area where we upload previous webinars and workshops.

Educate
Your Team

In the highly competitive agency space, demonstrating a commitment to educating your team and leveling up their skills goes a long way to retaining your best talent.

Help
Your Clients

Your agency’s specialism may be outside of SEO, but SUSO Partner Club gives you the extra SEO knowledge to help clients when they need your support.

A partnership designed for real results

“A super valuable resource for any agency. Our team loves the sessions.”
Jennifer (Sneyd) Mowat
Managing Director – Babel PR
“Our experience with the SUSO agency partner team has been superb from start to finish. Suso has provided top-notch SEO support whenever we needed it, and the recent partner training has delivered a step change in SEO knowledge across the agency.”
Olly Reed
Account Director – Navigate
“The free SEO reports we get for being a SUSO partner member are great. They’re much better than even the paid audits we’ve seen from other agencies. And the educational sessions have been really insightful, the team have learnt so much.”
Charlotte (Avis) Street
Delivery Director – The Escape
“The in-person training was excellent. The team learned new skills and an awareness of how SEO can positively impact our content strategies.”
Jo Fishburn
Client lead
“We’re traditionally a PPC and social agency, but we get many clients asking us about SEO. By educating ourselves through the SUSO partner club, we’re much better at speaking to our clients about the topic. SUSO have been great at helping us become a much more SEO-literate agency.”
Joe Brownrigg
Co-Founder – Ethix digital

Join the
SUSO Partner Club today

Grow your team’s SEO skills, help your agency stand out and drive results for your clients.

Sign up with your company name and contact details.

Join the SUSO Partner Club
